  "keyFeatures": [
    "Spring Boot 3 monolith on Java 21 with embedded Tomcat (ServerApplication)",
    "Multi-tenant data source routing via fineract.tenant.* properties",
    "Liquibase-managed tenant and tenant-store schemas (db/changelog)",
    "JAX-RS REST API exposed through Jersey (164 *ApiResource classes)",
    "Command bus (fineract-command) with sync, async, audit, disruptor and JDBC store variants",
    "Maker-checker workflow for write commands via commands/AuditsApiResource and MakercheckersApiResource",
    "Loan domain: fineract-loan (cumulative interest model)",
    "Progressive loan: fineract-progressive-loan with embeddable schedule generator",
    "Working capital loan: fineract-working-capital-loan with dedicated COB steps",
    "Loan origination: fineract-loan-origination (originators, enrichers, serialization)",
    "Savings, fixed deposit, recurring deposit and share products (fineract-savings)",
    "Accounting subsystem: GL accounts, journal entries, accruals, provisioning, financial activity",
    "Charges (fineract-charge), taxes (fineract-tax), floating rates (fineract-rates)",
    "Close of Business (fineract-cob) business-step framework with loan account locking",
    "Investor / external asset owner module (fineract-investor) for loan sales",
    "Background jobs registered via JobName enum and Quartz scheduler",
    "Spring Batch partitioned jobs (e.g. Loan COB, NPA update)",
    "Business events and external event producers (Kafka, ActiveMQ via docker-compose)",
    "Document management with pluggable content stores (filesystem, S3) and detectors",
    "Reports (Pentaho), Run Reports, Report Mailing Job, Ad-hoc Query, MIX taxonomy",
    "SMS and Email campaigns with scheduler + gateway",
    "Credit bureau integration (creditbureau)",
    "Interoperation (Mojaloop) API resource",
    "Survey & SPM (Social Performance Management) scorecard",
    "Two-factor authentication (twofactor-tests project)",
    "OAuth2 client/server support (oauth2-tests project)",
    "fineract-client and fineract-client-feign generated SDKs",
    "fineract-avro-schemas for external events",
    "fineract-e2e-tests-core/runner Cucumber/Gherkin suite (~123 feature files)",
    "Docker, docker-compose (PostgreSQL/MySQL/MariaDB/Kafka/ActiveMQ) and Kubernetes manifests",
    "Custom module dynamic loading via custom/<company>/<category>/<module> directory layout",
    "Bulk import (Excel populators + handlers) and templating engine",
    "Resilience4j retry configuration per command type",
    "Static weaving for EclipseLink JPA entities",
    "fineract-validation custom Bean Validation constraints",
    "fineract-doc Antora documentation modules",
    "fineract-war traditional WAR packaging"
  ],
  "publicApiSurface": [
    "fineract-provider/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/ServerApplication.java",
    "fineract-provider/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/infrastructure/core/boot/FineractWebApplicationConfiguration.java",
